# Items list – all items or ingredients only (REST Client)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5100

### Default – all items (excludes water item, includes category + allowedUnits + recipeCount)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items

### Explicit mode=all (same as default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items?mode=all

### Ingredients only (excludes house category; for recipe filters / create recipe)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items?mode=ingredients
